{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2016}} {{Use British English|date=August 2016}} [[File:Actor_Harvey_Braban.jpg|thumb|right|Braban as [[Florizel (The Winter's Tale)|Florizel]] in a stage production of Shakespeare's ''[[The Winter's Tale]]'', c. 1910<ref>{{cite web|url=https://shakespeare.emory.edu/harvey-braban/winters_christine_braban_01_front-2/|title=Harvey Braban and Lilian Christine in “The Winter’s Tale” - Shakespeare and the Players|website=shakespeare.emory.edu}}</ref>]] '''Harvey Braban''' (19 May 1883, [[Brighton]], [[Sussex]], UK - 1943) was a British [[stage actor]].<ref name=theatricalia>{{cite web|url=https://theatricalia.com/person/dak/harvey-braban/past|title=Harvey Braban - Theatricalia|website=theatricalia.com}}</ref> He also appeared in films between 1920-1938.<ref name=bfi>{{cite web|url=http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/17370?view=credit|title=Harvey Braban|publisher=}}</ref>
